    • bound

      protected float bound​(java.lang.Integer currentVertex, java.util.ArrayList<TupleRequete> requetes)
      Computes a lower bound of the length of the path left to travel to complete all remaining Requests. Returns the sum of the lengths of the paths from each node to its closest successor.
      Specified by:
      bound in class Template_BnB_TSP
      Parameters:
      currentVertex - The index of the current node (interest point)
      requetes - The list of Requests left to deal with
      Returns:
      a lower bound of the cost of paths in matAdj starting from currentVertex, visiting every interest point in requetes, and returning back to vertex 0.
